subject: Figure Skating
Costumes, Theatrical
Olympic Games (2010)
lead_paragraph: Lilac vinyl jumpsuits, sheer tops, off-the-shoulder necklines, corsets, tassels, feathers and fur are all the rage in skating costumes. And then there are the women.
